01:07:12,019 --> 01:07:13,760
"Pusat Kanker"

1057
01:07:14,019 --> 01:07:15,089
Ayah.

1058
01:07:16,030 --> 01:07:17,830
Kenapa kemari?

1059
01:07:21,930 --> 01:07:23,970
Keadaan di rumah baik-baik saja?

1060
01:07:23,970 --> 01:07:24,970
Tidak.

1061
01:07:27,470 --> 01:07:28,709
Apa Eun Tae

1062
01:07:32,510 --> 01:07:33,879
